{"tw": {"4120350": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "The Power of Truth - Book 1", "steam_appid": 4120350, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4120350/extras/f28ceb000bd36c8500fa5882f803306e.avif?t=1776055795\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4120350/extras_big/f28ceb000bd36c8500fa5882f803306e.avif?t=1776055795 width=1560 height=390 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>He’s brilliant. Respected. Desired. But behind every lecture lies a question that haunts him…</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At Infinity College, he’s the vice president and star professor—charismatic, sharp, and effortlessly successful. But no amount of prestige can silence the one truth he can’t escape:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>He doesn’t know who he is.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4120350/extras/418ac846e699abf9f17370d30b49dab0.avif?t=1776055795\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4120350/extras_big/418ac846e699abf9f17370d30b49dab0.avif?t=1776055795 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Raised in foster homes. No records. No roots.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not dead. Just… vanished.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now, the man who’s taught the best of the best to seek answers embarks on a journey to find his own. A search for identity that will unravel more than he ever expected—leading him through a world of secrets, sex, danger, and deception.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4120350/extras/34aae0a3d63c1e9a013b99331722efb2.avif?t=1776055795\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4120350/extras_big/34aae0a3d63c1e9a013b99331722efb2.avif?t=1776055795 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4120350/extras/a7ebf51a7f87c52fd79b3daa07572d10.avif?t=1776055795\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4120350/extras_big/a7ebf51a7f87c52fd79b3daa07572d10.avif?t=1776055795 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Haunted by flashes of a life he can’t remember and a growing fear that he wasn’t just abandoned… was he... designed?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Power of Truth—When the Past Is a Lie, What Will You Believe?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock the mystery. Rewrite your destiny.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4120350/extras/c94805587a91d8fa698661f5b0b5c9c9.avif?t=1776055795\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4120350/extras_big/c94805587a91d8fa698661f5b0b5c9c9.avif?t=1776055795 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Power of Truth is not a harem game and offers multiple routes. The MC isn't committed to any girl unless he chooses, as a past event left him wary of commitment—a decision he’ll only make later in the game. Until then, he’s free to engage with any girl he likes. Some are open to threesomes, while others prefer exclusivity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4120350/extras/3085cb565d847ac00c76bb99dcf3bd60.avif?t=1776055795\" width=700 height=87 />