pps/4120350/extras_big/418ac846e699abf9f17370d30b49dab0.avif?t=1776055795 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Raised in foster homes. No records. No roots.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not dead. Just… vanished.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now, the man who’s taught the best of the best to seek answers embarks on a journey to find his own. A search for identity that will unravel more than he ever expected—leading him through a world of secrets, sex, danger, and deception.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4120350/extras/34aae0a3d63c1e9a013b99331722efb2.avif?t=1776055795\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4120350/extras_big/34aae0a3d63c1e9a013b99331722efb2.avif?t=1776055795 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4120350/extras/a7ebf51a7f87c52fd79b3daa07572d10.avif?t=1776055795\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4120350/extras_big/a7ebf51a7f87c52fd79b3daa07572d10.avif?t=1776055795 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Haunted by flashes of a life he can’t remember and a growing fear that he wasn’t just abandoned… was he... designed?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Power of Truth—When the Past Is a Lie, What Will You Believe?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock the mystery. Rewrite your destiny.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4120350/extras/c94805587a91d8fa698661f5b0b5c9c9.avif?t=1776055795\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4120350/extras_big/c94805587a91d8fa698661f5b0b5c9c9.avif?t=1776055795 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Power of Truth is not a harem game and offers multiple routes. The MC isn't committed to any girl unless he chooses, as a past event left him wary of commitment—a decision he’ll only make later in the game. Until then, he’s free to engage with any girl he likes. Some are open to threesomes, while others prefer exclusivity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4120350/extras/3085cb565d847ac00c76bb99dcf3bd60.avif?t=1776055795\" width=700 height=87 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visuals: ~<strong>7000 </strong>visuals rendered in 2K resolution</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Animations: ~<strong>100 </strong>in 2K/30fps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music tracks: ~<strong>90</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SFX: <strong>~100</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Power of Truth offers a unique mechanism to spice up the MC's personality. Choices will lock/unlock scenes/sub-scenes. Will you be a gentleman or a pervert?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4120350/extras/f878447f05554a2726abe15555a08812.avif?t=1776055795\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4120350/extras_big/f878447f05554a2726abe15555a08812.avif?t=1776055795 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Power of Truth is packed with NSFW content, and animations are rendered at 2K/30fps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_a